📋 Overview
TaskFlow is a modern, full-stack task and project management application that combines the power of the MERN stack with intelligent AI assistance. Built with a focus on user experience, it offers a seamless way to organize, track, and complete your tasks efficiently.

Whether you're managing personal projects, collaborating with teams, or organizing your daily workflow, TaskFlow provides the tools you need to stay productive and organized.

------------------------
     Key Features
------------------------
🔐Authentication System
User registration with name, email, and password
Login with JWT token-based authentication
Password hashing using bcryptjs
Protected routes for authenticated users
Logout functionality

📊 Dashboard
Display total tasks count
Show completed tasks statistics
Display in-progress tasks
Show overdue tasks count
Quick view of user's boards
Board progress indicators
Create new board button

📋 Board Management
Create new boards with title and description
View all boards in a grid layout
Edit board title and description
Delete boards with confirmation
Board progress tracking (task completion percentage)
Task count per board
Due this week task count

✅ Task Management
Create tasks with title, description, priority, due date, and effort estimate
Three status columns: To Do, In Progress, Done
Edit task details
Delete tasks with confirmation
Priority levels: Low, Medium, High (color-coded)
Due date tracking with overdue indication
Effort estimation in hours
Task cards display: title, priority badge, due date, effort estimate

🤖 AI Feature - Smart Estimation
"Suggest Estimate" button on task creation
Sends task title and description to Google Gemini API
Returns suggested effort (in hours) and recommended due date
Shows reasoning for the suggestion
User can accept or reject the suggestion

🎨 UI/UX Features
Dark/Light Mode Toggle with persisted preference
Responsive Design - Works on mobile, tablet, and desktop
Clean Sidebar Navigation with icons
Modern Card-based Layout
Smooth Animations using Framer Motion


