📁 Project Structure
taskflow/
├── server/                      # Backend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── config/
│   │   │   ├── database.js     # MongoDB connection
│   │   │   └── constants.js    # App constants (status, priority)
│   │   ├── models/
│   │   │   ├── User.js         # User schema with bcrypt hashing
│   │   │   ├── Board.js        # Board schema with owner reference
│   │   │   └── Task.js         # Task schema with status, priority
│   │   ├── controllers/
│   │   │   ├── authController.js    # Register, login, getMe
│   │   │   ├── boardController.js   # CRUD operations for boards
│   │   │   └── taskController.js    # CRUD + AI suggestion
│   │   ├── routes/
│   │   │   ├── authRoutes.js        # /api/auth endpoints
│   │   │   ├── boardRoutes.js       # /api/boards endpoints
│   │   │   └── taskRoutes.js        # /api/tasks endpoints
│   │   ├── middleware/
│   │   │   ├── auth.js         # JWT verification middleware
│   │   │   └── errorHandler.js # Global error handling
│   │   ├── ai/
│   │   │   └── geminiService.js # Google Gemini API integration
│   │   └── server.js           # Main server file
│   ├── .env.example            # Environment variables template
│   └── package.json            # Backend dependencies
│
├── client/                      # Frontend
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   ├── Layout/
│   │   │   │   ├── Layout.jsx      # Main layout wrapper
│   │   │   │   ├── Sidebar.jsx     # Navigation sidebar
│   │   │   │   └── Header.jsx      # Top header with user info
│   │   │   ├── TaskCard.jsx        # Task card with drag handle
│   │   │   ├── TaskModal.jsx       # Create/Edit task modal
│   │   │   └── AISuggestionModal.jsx # AI suggestion modal
│   │   ├── pages/
│   │   │   ├── Login.jsx           # Login page
│   │   │   ├── Register.jsx        # Registration page
│   │   │   ├── Dashboard.jsx       # Dashboard with stats
│   │   │   ├── Boards.jsx          # Boards management page
│   │   │   └── BoardDetail.jsx     # Board view with tasks
│   │   ├── services/
│   │   │   ├── api.js              # Axios client with interceptors
│   │   │   ├── authService.js      # Auth API calls
│   │   │   ├── boardService.js     # Board API calls
│   │   │   └── taskService.js      # Task API calls
│   │   ├── context/
│   │   │   ├── AuthContext.jsx     # Authentication state
│   │   │   └── ThemeContext.jsx    # Dark/Light mode state
│   │   ├── App.jsx                 # Main app with routing
│   │   ├── main.jsx                # Entry point
│   │   └── index.css               # Global styles with Tailwind
│   ├── .env.example
│   ├── package.json
│   └── tailwind.config.js
│
├── .gitignore
└── README.md


📡 API Endpoints Implemented
--Authentication Routes
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/auth/register	Register new user
POST	/api/auth/login	Login user
GET	/api/auth/me	Get current user (Protected)
PUT	/api/auth/preferences	Update user preferences (Protected)

--Board Routes (Protected)
Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	/api/boards	Get all boards with task counts
POST	/api/boards	Create new board
PUT	/api/boards/:id	Update board
DELETE	/api/boards/:id	Delete board and its tasks

--Task Routes (Protected)
Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	/api/tasks/board/:boardId	Get tasks by board
POST	/api/tasks	Create new task
PUT	/api/tasks/:id	Update task
DELETE	/api/tasks/:id	Delete task
POST	/api/tasks/suggest	Get AI suggestion

